{"tid":325282,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"糖妹唱《如何掉眼淚》 網民大讚眼前一亮","createTime":"2017-07-17T06:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T06:02:17.000Z","uid":14730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a98d458281b107e80d3a8b152a125fac8671e38","tid":325282,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T06:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/140118_759b4b50a8b8a6088cf27bda4d7a5cea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F140118_759b4b50a8b8a6088cf27bda4d7a5cea.jpg&h=c3ee0c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚大台播出的《流行經典50年》請來胡美儀、Joe Junior和柳影紅等份量級歌手，不過新一代歌手如王浩信、譚嘉儀和糖妹憑實力唱功亦不比一眾前輩輸蝕，前者一起合唱無限loop的《陪着你走》；後者就翻唱天后鄭秀文唱的《如何掉眼淚》，喚起大家青春回憶的同事，不少網民大讚糖妹唱功一流，更加令人眼前一一亮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uucQgZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uucQgZ&d=lPKRRz6ssMTRD7aqGbf%2B%2FU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=c415db6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uucQgZ</a>"}]}